data.description: More than meets the eye! This expansive property, tucked away for ultimate privacy, boasts a fully renovated kitchen, modern bathrooms, 4 bedrooms, loads of natural light and potential for 2 separate rental units. Long recently paved driveway lined with brand new belgium block. With a detached 2-car garage, it's versatile and functional. The stunning lake views, coupled with the option to add a pool, make this a unique gem. Enjoy rights to Putnam Lake where you can swim or spend your time on a kayak, row boat or electric boat. Dual street access adds convenience and endless potential. It's more than just a home; it's a canvas for your dreams. Discover this exceptional opportunity today!
